videos.description: Damian Lillard avoids the double-team with a step-back move, then pulls up to snap the net as he drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Lillard drains smooth step-back 3

videos.description: Derrick Jones Jr. does a Eurostep on his way to the basket and throws up a shot that somehow goes in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Derrick Jones Eurosteps to the basket throws up circus shot) 2021/3/4 ESHEET

videos.headline: Derrick Jones Eurosteps to the basket, throws up circus shot

videos.description: Damian Lillard comes alive late in the fourth quarter by hitting back-to-back 3-pointers.
